item.title: How did the Blue Bloods fare from the 2020 season to 2021?
item.description: The 2021 College Basketball season has been hard for many especially with the COVID-19 pandemic.We have seen many teams struggle even for the Blue Bloods of league. This season we saw some of the best teams digress and not compete at the level that fans have seen them in the past. Duke and Kentucky are the top headlines as how they have struggled and each finished their seasons below .

item.title: About Jake Janousek
item.description: I am a Sophomore at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln. I am a double major in Sports Media and Commutation and Broadcasting with a minor in Political Science. My favorite thing in the world is obviously Sports. One day I hope to be in the broadcasting game as a play by play or radio host for any sports show. Other things I like to do is be around my family and friends.

item.title: Another Note on A blogdown Tutorial
